headline: Textron Aviation Calls on Cessna, Beechcraft and Hawker Owners to Transport Athletes to the 2026 Special Olympics USA Games
summary: WICHITA, Kan., May 01, 2025--Textron Aviation announced the ninth Special Olympics Airlift, aimed at transporting athletes and coaches to the 2026 Special Olympics USA Games.
